But when I used the debug mode to trace (steps through) the code, the NPE never happen. Maybe we need a synchronized artifactEdit.dispose()?

    try    {
      artifactEdit = WsbndArtifactEdit.getWSBNDArtifactEditForWrite(ibmWsBndXmiProject);
